            "id": 6272002,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉SpaceX明年上市點火太空題材 漲173點收28198點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股昨 (11) 日如搭大怒神，創高後終場收黑，今 (12) 日電子權值股漲跌互現，不過台積電僅小有表態，大盤終場漲 173.27 或 0.62%，以 28198.02 點作收，未能站穩 5 日線，成交量 4748.06 億元。今天盤面亮點，則轉為聚焦太空、線纜及重電族群。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6272002/l/fd670b2729ac0bcdb83ebd4446f0c580.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股盤後〉SpaceX明年上市點火太空題材 漲173點收28198點。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股今天漲跌互現，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 小漲 10 元，收 1480 元，漲幅 0.68%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 漲 0.44%，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 漲 0.72%，不過台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 跌 0.74%，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 跌 0.52%，日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 跌 0.41%。 </p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>太空商機升空，馬斯克證實 SpaceX 明年將上市，SpaceX 供應鏈齊走揚，元晶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6443-TW</a>)、大眾控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3701:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3701\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3701-TW</a>) 漲停鎖死，事欣科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4916:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4916\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4916-TW</a>)、昇達科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3491:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3491\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3491-TW</a>) 漲逾半根停板，正文 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4906:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4906\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4906-TW</a>)、兆赫 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2485:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2485\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2485-TW</a>) 則漲逾 2%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國聯準會宣布降息 1 碼，並上修美國經濟成長預測，銅價隨之攀升，激勵線纜族群今天走揚，華新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1605-TW</a>) 大漲逾半根停板，華榮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1608:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1608\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1608-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%，大亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1609-TW</a>)、億泰 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1616:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1616\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1616-TW</a>) 皆漲逾 2%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>重電族群今天表現同樣強勢，華城 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1519:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1519\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1519-TW</a>) 法說會前股價先行暖身，大漲逾半根停板，大同 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2371:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2371\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2371-TW</a>)、東元 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1504:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1504\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1504-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，亞力 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1514:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1514\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1514-TW</a>)、士電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1503:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1503\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1503-TW</a>) 及中興電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1513:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1513\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1513-TW</a>) 則有超過 2% 漲幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
